---
title: BBQ Pulled Pork Sandwiches with Red Cabbage Slaw
description: It’s tough to resist the saucy, tender texture and tangy flavor of BBQ pulled pork. Here, it stars in sandwiches that come together in just 15 minutes. For this lightning-speed meal, you’ll mix your slaw, warm your pulled pork with zesty Southwest spices, and pile it all onto toasted potato buns. Just think: you’re that much closer to sandwich bliss.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/southwest-bbq-pulled-pork-sandwiches-ebf4041f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/bbq-pulled-pork-sandwiches-606cb378dd87867e3b30b170-648725b0.pdf
time required: 15 minutes
servings: 2
cuisine: North America
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/bbq-pulled-pork-sandwiches-606cb378dd87867e3b30b170
author: HelloFresh
